      "content": "interesting. so u say it was co-opted to dismiss unfavorable coverage... but isn't it also true that there's actually a lot of bad info out there being pumped out by certain outlets? like, is \"fake news\" just a label people use to shut down critics, or is there an actual difference between \"biased\" media and stuff that's just straight up lying?",
